e of the bound state deep inside the conducting pore and,\nthus, to play an unexpected but significant role in aquaglyceroporin's\nfunctions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 22 Sep 2012 17:47:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-03-13"}
